title: Beautiful Craftsman on exceptional lot in most desireable neighborhood
posting_body: ['Highly desirable Old Palo Alto neighborhood.', ' Exceptional 16,500 sq ft lot.', ' Spacious open floor plan.', ' Perfect for entertaining or a private quiet retreat.', ' Walking distance to all the amenities of Downtown, Cal Ave, and Midtown Palo Alto.', 'Traditional Craftsman quality with expertly upgraded kitchen and bathrooms.', ' Large open floor plan, big bay windows and beautiful surrounding porches.', ' Lush private gardens, three fireplaces, sunny backyard.', ' Detached cottage with fireplace and bathroom.', ' Beautiful original white oak floors.', ' Centrally located to Palo Alto schools, walking or biking distance.', ' (Tenant to verify PA schools.)']
